== 製作 ==
[[Netflix|Netflix]]於2019年9月3日公佈影集第一季6集的製作，由 {{Link-en|傑森·喬治|Jason George}}和原作小說作者{{Link-en|傑西克·杜卡|Jacek Dukaj}}擔任製片人<ref name="SeriesOrder">{{Cite web|last=White|first=Peter|title=Netflix Orders First Belgian Original 'Into The Night' From 'Narcos' & 'Scandal' Producer Jason George|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/netflix-orders-first-belgian-original-into-the-night-from-narcos-producer-jason-george-1202709451/|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=September 3, 2019}}</ref>，並於9月30日開拍。<ref name="Filming">{{cite web|title=NETFLIX ANNOUNCES THE CAST FOR INTO THE NIGHT|url=https://media.netflix.com/en/press-releases/netflix-announces-the-cast-for-into-the-night|work=[[Netflix_Media_Center|Netflix Media Center]]|date=September 30, 2019}}</ref>

2020年4月24日於[[Netflix|Netflix]]網站播放預告片<ref name="Trailer">{{Cite web|last=Millican|first=Josh|title=Try to Outrun the Sun in Trailer for INTO THE NIGHT, Arriving on Netflix May 1st|url=https://www.dreadcentral.com/news/325268/try-to-outrun-the-sun-in-trailer-for-into-the-night-arriving-on-netflix-may-1st/|work=[[Dread_Central|Dread Central]]|date=April 25, 2020}}</ref>，並於5月1日開始連載。由於評價正面，[[Netflix|Netflix]]於7月1日宣布拍攝第二季。<ref name="Season 2">{{Cite web|title=Into the Night Season 2|url=https://www.vitalthrills.com/into-the-night-season-2-given-the-green-light-by-netflix/
|work=ViralThrills|date=July 1, 2020}}</ref>。

